多警務人員進入監房時，真的要看他是什麼職級，愈高級，處理要小心。當有較高級的「帆船牌」要從一個囚室到另一個地方，例如拜山（探監）或者見律師的時候，很多時都會找幫辦負責帶領。<br />\n<br />\n令我印象較深刻的是，當一些「帆船牌」和一般囚犯碰面時，「帆船牌」一點驚慌也沒有，很多囚犯更和他們打招呼，相信，這些前警察真的不需要保護。從前警察口中得知，其實他們是和這些「古惑仔」是有「打鑼」的（較密切往來) ，可說成互相利用，有沒有金錢利益就不得而知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱話/146330/警司淪為階下囚-一碟冷飯-兩句冷語-懲教人員面前流下男兒淚\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F146330%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%B8%E6%B7%AA%E7%82%BA%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%8B%E5%9B%9A-%E4%B8%80%E7%A2%9F%E5%86%B7%E9%A3%AF-%E5%85%A9%E5%8F%A5%E5%86%B7%E8%AA%9E-%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E9%9D%A2%E5%89%8D%E6%B5%81%E4%B8%8B%E7%94%B7%E5%85%92%E6%B7%9A&d=n2QiVH5lzydu35rodligO49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5b366b2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱話/146330/警司淪為階下囚-一碟冷飯-兩句冷語-懲教人員面前流下男兒淚</a>"},{"pid":"3d49e92cb17ad3d102e163614facd20c8034657e","tid":522942,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"按章工作 拉喇仲唔拉"},{"pid":"a51f2a34cc71bb3269a93e388089963006d19102","tid":522942,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ddf877293e8c8c36972f0e5b7cf73386b0eec1","tid":522942,"uid":46587,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"泛民收工都去建制派啲酒席啦<br />\n收左工就做下朋友有咩所謂噃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b297433efa13d2ecf21e83f316765bc25b429680","tid":522942,"uid":67283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"477c6b1dbccaf74c29031267023150920c1ab3d0","tid":522942,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"實捉到你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜東方近牌變左反政府既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T05:17:47.000Z","msg":"今朝頭